{
 "name": "RPlog_Secret_Service_Supper",
 "title": "Secret Service Supper",
 "summary": "Aboard the Caspian flagship Leviathan, the Presav Crestian hosts an intimate dinner of homemade glowblue noodles for two of his Mandalorian agents, Rawnie Qrowe and Nara Rhen, joined by the intelligence figures Zubindi Hakoon, Veruca Violet, and the precocious near-ten-year-old Atsvara Tarasar. Over the meal the group trades warm banter about covers and craft -- Rawnie's engineering snooping and armor-fitting, Nara's flourishing socialite persona, and the art of building cover identities that take on lives of their own. Crestian muses on cooking as a tool for crew morale while the agents discuss the new fighters' over-tuned compensators and the value of an organically convincing cover. The supper culminates in Zubindi and Veruca promoting Nara to Field Agent and advancing her credits, and the table toasts to those who walk in shadow to protect those who do not.",
